murder, and alternately charm, fight, or sprint their way out of

it's cars, peace of mind, or daughters. Marie-Ange, a jaded, passive 
hairdresser, joins them as lover, cook, and mother confessor. She's 
on her own search for seemingly unattainable sexual pleasure.
